    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美国经济面临“过渡时期”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-10/trump-says-us-economy-to-face-period-of-transition-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周日对降低速度的风险表示关注，称美国经济面临“过渡时期”，因为他早期对关税和联邦工作的关注会导致市场动荡。凯文·惠特拉（Kevin Whitelaw）在彭博电视台上报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-10/trump-says-us-economy-to-face-period-of-transition-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 10:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威财富基金顾问警告我们可能会阻碍腐败工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/norway-wealth-fund-adviser-warns-us-may-hinder-corruption-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威1.8万亿美元主权财富基金的道德委员会警告说，美国反腐败立法的撤销可能会使确定违反道德准则的企业更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/norway-wealth-fund-adviser-warns-us-may-hinder-corruption-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西亿万富翁家庭竞标接管法国的Verallia</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/brazil-billionaire-family-bids-to-take-over-france-s-verallia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西的亿万富翁莫雷拉·萨尔斯（Moreira Salles）家族正在竞标，以接管法国包装公司Verallia SA，如果其主要投资更好地导致贸易紧张局势越来越上升，则可以帮助一个人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/brazil-billionaire-family-bids-to-take-over-france-s-verallia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 09:51:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普过渡谈话燃烧衰退焦虑时，国库会获得</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/treasuries-gain-as-trump-transition-talk-fuels-recession-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普总统对美国经济的“过渡时期”的评论，国库会集会，这加剧了人们担心放缓可能在拐角处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/treasuries-gain-as-trump-transition-talk-fuels-recession-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 09:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
